
Todays Soft Skill Tip:

Day 37: Word Power Rule - Swap Weak Words With Strong Ones

Most people don’t lack confidence…
their words do.

Replace: “I think / maybe / I guess”
With: “I believe / I recommend / Based on this…”

Instant upgrade in how people see you.

Task for Today:
Rewrite one sentence you use daily into a stronger version.

Strong words create a strong impression.
